{
  "stem": "26728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never did see the results of that, but it must have been devastating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We must have killed thousands of people, and soldiers, and burnt tanks, and half tracks, and trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- it was just five or six miles of just fire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just kept it going with incendiary bombs, incendiary ammunition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, we went back to Luneville.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was about, probably February, March, February maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or no, earlier than that-- January of '45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By then, they were going into Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went down to the Saar Basin, and the name of the town that rings-- there's three towns that ring a bell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Petite Rochelle, which was in Alsace Lorraine-- Grande Rochelle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they're just a little crossroad towns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Forbach, France, which is a monument is there-- put there by the French people for the 70th Division, which had been formerly my home unit, who liberated that part of France.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I've been back to reunions there and-- and met with some of the fellows that I served with here in Oregon as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg you pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forbach?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "F-o-r-b-a-c-h.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's quite a-- there is quite a-- quite a history around that whole area of tremendous battle that took place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought in some SS, the Germans brought in some SS mountain-- now German, you don't ordinarily fight SS people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, these were-- they were special troops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in this particular battle for-- [INAUDIBLE] Saarland, which I got a citation for-- well, we all did-- was a battle called Nordwind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans named the battle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was kind of a mini Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was winter of '44 and '45.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and it was-- it was a terrible battle, terrible for both sides.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
